'From Squeak2.8alpha of 16 February 2000 [latest update: #1940] on 19 March 2000 at 2:15:41 pm'!"Change Set:		ThreeDSFixes-arDate:			19 March 2000Author:			Andreas RaabTwo small orientation fixes for 3DS import."!!B3DCamera methodsFor: 'initialize' stamp: 'ar 3/19/2000 14:12'!from3DS: aDictionary	"Initialize the receiver from a 3DS camera.	Note: #near and #far are NOT clipping planes in 3DS!!"	self position: (aDictionary at: #position).	self target: (aDictionary at: #target).	self up: (0@1@0).	self flag: #TODO. "Include #roll value for upDirection"	self fieldOfView: 2400.0 / (aDictionary at: #focal).! !!ThreeDSParser methodsFor: 'reading-primitives' stamp: 'ar 3/19/2000 14:12'!vector3	"Generic Subchunk containing a vector"	| x y z |	x _ self float.	"Swap z and y"	z _ self float.	y _ self float.	^B3DVector3 x: x y: y z: z! !